<item>
            <title>[HBASE-4037] Add timeout annotations to preempt surefire killing all tests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4037</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Let me add the timeout annotation to a few of the tests that are currently without them and that go on so long, the maven surefire plugin steps in and kills the whole test run (Comes of discussion up on mailing list: &lt;a href=&quot;http://search-hadoop.com/m/ALF0L1yBgA5/Build+failed+in+Jenkins%253A+HBase-TRUNK+%25231989&amp;amp;subj=Re+Build+failed+in+Jenkins+HBase+TRUNK+1892&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://search-hadoop.com/m/ALF0L1yBgA5/Build+failed+in+Jenkins%253A+HBase-TRUNK+%25231989&amp;amp;subj=Re+Build+failed+in+Jenkins+HBase+TRUNK+1892&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
