                            <comment id="13068831" author="stack" created="Thu, 21 Jul 2011 06:42:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Enough commits have been made under this umbrella.  Resolving (TRUNK build is  blue every other time and the failures because of 15 minute timeouts haven&apos;t been seen in a while &amp;#8211; we seem to have gotten the current crop of timeouties).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15016548" author="lars_francke" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2015 11:55:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This issue was closed as part of a bulk closing operation on 2015-11-20. All issues that have been resolved and where all fixVersions have been released have been closed (following discussions on the mailing list).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
